These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, pepper, potato
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, begonia, amaryllis
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, writer, entrepreneur
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, aristoff, ritmeester
1. the person eating pepper is between the person who growsdahlia and the prince-smoker##2
2. the scientist is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Food          | corn      | pepper        | potato     |
| Flower         | amaryllis | begonia | dahlia    |
| Job   | writer   | scientist       | entrepreneur |
| Cigar         | prince  | aristoff      | ritmeester    |

