.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, coach, photographer
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, blood-red, azure
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, begonia, daffodil
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, bus, trike
1. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is the coach##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
4. the coach is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the photographer##3
6. the photographer is in an even position##4
7. the person driving the trike is between the person who likes blood-red and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | coach    | photographer | accountant |
| Color   | blood-red | ebony       | azure   |
| Flower           | daffodil  | begonia   | tulip     |
| Transport         | bus | trike       | boat   |

