.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, milk
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, orchid
3 different pets are kept: bird, pony, turtle
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, punk, dubstep
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the fan of techno##1
2. the person drinking milk is the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who growspoppy and the fan of dubstep##2
5. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the turtle is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage          | milk | soy-milk | fanta |
| Flower   | orchid     | rose | poppy |
| Pet           | pony       | bird   | turtle    |
| Music-Genre     | dubstep      | techno   | punk |

