.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
House: ranch-style, victorian, cape-cod
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, van, jet-ski
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, swisher, prince
There are 3 different nationalities: british, italian, pakistani
1. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the swisher-smoker##1
4. the italian is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the italian is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| House         | victorian  | ranch-style       | cape-cod |
| Transport           | jet-ski     | van      | airplane   |
| Cigar   | swisher | pall-mall | prince     |
| Nationality   | british      | pakistani   | italian     |

