The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, salsa, soul
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, boat
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the fan of pop##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
7. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Flower      | sunflower     | amaryllis   | dahlia         |
| Pet           | hedgehog | fish | turtle |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | salsa   | pop            |
| Transport   | skateboard   | boat  | bus         |

