The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, crime, zombie
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid, aconite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, skateboarding, lacrosse
1. the egyptian is in the middle##1
2. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the egyptian##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
5. the french is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
6. the person who growslily is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the indonesian##2
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Nationality          | indonesian | egyptian | french |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | action    | zombie |
| Flower   | orchid  | lily   | aconite    |
| Sport     | lacrosse   | badminton       | skateboarding |

