House: modern, ranch-style, gothic-revival
There are 3 different nationalities: german, pakistani, russian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, r&b, punk
1. the russian is on the far left or far right##3
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the havana-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of r&b is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the left of the pakistani##1
6. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
7. the modern house is between the pakistani and the fan of punk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Cigar      | havana | old-henry    | vegafina  |
| House         | gothic-revival        | modern   | ranch-style   |
| Nationality   | russian       | german    | pakistani |
| Music-Genre     | punk          | r&b | folk       |

