3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, vegafina, tiparillo
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the fan of classical is the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of classical is the palace house##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
6. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4
7. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
