.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, sprite
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, bike, boat
City: hannover, miami, rome
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, may
1. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bike is the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the person driving the boat is the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | juice      | almond-milk  |
| Transport          | bike     | boat | helicopter       |
| City   | hannover  | rome    | miami      |
| Birthday         | may | july  | april |

