3 different games are played: whist, backgammon, go
House: victorian, modern, cape-cod
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the victorian house is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
4. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
5. the modern house is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person traveling to nizza is between the person traveling to hamburg and the victorian house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| City      | rome       | nizza   | hamburg |
| Game   | whist | go     | backgammon |
| House           | victorian      | modern | cape-cod    |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | soccer     | biathlon |

