There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, azure, black
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
3. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who likes black##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who likes black##1
9. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Cigar           | davidoff | blend   | cain |
| Flower   | amaryllis  | begonia    | dahlia    |
| Sport         | cricket    | badminton | parkour   |
| Color     | azure  | black     | light-blue  |

