.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, reading, video-games
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, ship, taxi
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, d&b, ambient
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, fantasy
1. the fan of blues is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person watching musical movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching mystery movies is between the person driving the taxi and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby         | video-games    | reading   | puzzles      |
| Transport           | taxi | scooter    | ship |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | d&b | ambient      |
| Movie-Genre         | fantasy         | mystery   | musical     |

