.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-17::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, nectarine, onion
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, pony, horse
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, fanta
3 different games are played: scrabble, go, monopoly
1. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
2. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating nectarine and the person playing monopoly##2
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
6. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Food          | onion     | cauliflower | nectarine   |
| Pet         | horse   | chinchilla | pony |
| Beverage   | fanta | tea       | hot-chocolate   |
| Game     | monopoly     | scrabble  | go        |

