.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, baking, traveling
3 different games are played: chess, billiard, monopoly
There are 3 different nationalities: french, mexican, pakistani
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, cola
1. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
2. the mexican is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the pakistani is in an even position##4
6. the person playing chess is the mexican##1
7. the french is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is baking is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Hobby          | baking  | collecting   | traveling |
| Game   | billiard      | monopoly      | chess   |
| Nationality   | french     | pakistani | mexican |
| Beverage         | tea | almond-milk   | cola   |

