.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
There 3 different types of food: onion, pumpkin, cabbage
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, fonseca, ritmeester
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, skiing, cricket
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Food           | onion  | cabbage | pumpkin   |
| Cigar   | fonseca | ritmeester           | montecristo      |
| Sport           | cricket   | skiing          | handball |
| Transport     | boat    | tram           | snowmobile |

 